# - Try to find Sqlite
# Once done this will define
#
#  SQLITE_FOUND - system has Sqlite
#  SQLITE_INCLUDE_DIR - the Sqlite include directory
#  SQLITE_LIBRARIES - Link these to use Sqlite
#  SQLITE_MIN_VERSION - The minimum SQLite version
